#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.floor_divide.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.floor\\_divide"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv:1 of
msgid ""
"Return the largest integer smaller or equal to the division of the "
"inputs. It is equivalent to the Python ``//`` operator and pairs with the"
" Python ``%`` (`remainder`), function so that ``b = a % b + b * (a // "
"b)`` up to roundoff."
msgstr ""
"返回小于或等于输入除法结果的最大整数。它等价于 Python 的 ``//`` 运算符，"
"并与 Python 的 ``%``（`remainder`）函数配对使用，满足 ``b = a % b + b * ("
"a // b)`` （忽略舍入误差）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv:6 of
msgid "Numerator."
msgstr "分子。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv:8 of
msgid "Denominator."
msgstr "分母。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv:10 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated array is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，它必须具有可广播至输入形状的形状。如果未"
"提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的数组。元组（仅可作为关键字参数）的长度"
"必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv:15 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "为 True 的值表示在该位置计算 ufunc，为 False 的值表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.floordiv.floordiv:20 of
msgid "**y** -- y = floor(`x1`/`x2`)"
msgstr ""

